            <title>[CAMEL-6627] Splitter should close iterator if there was an exception and stopOnException enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6627</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See nabble&lt;br/&gt;
